HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO ME!! 
So blessed to see another year, I’m thankful for all of it. The high, the low, the blessings,the lessons, the setbacks, the comebacks, the love, the hate. Everything. 

Dear wiser me 
Thank you for being yourself. Thank you for showing me that bad days are actually the best one’s because those are the ones that show you how strong you are . Thank you for pushing through every obstacle and not choosing a bad way out. Thank you for showing me how real friends will love you unconditionally. Thank you for showing me what love feels like. Thank you for showing me that it’s okay to be a mess and still be beautiful. Thank you for showing me that it’s okay to ask for help. Thank you for showing me it’s okay to not be okay. Dear wiser self, if it wasn’t for you i wouldn’t be here . So thank you

I hope you realize how beautiful you are. And I hope you realize what you deserve. I hope you realize you are your own healer. That you can overcome anything. And come out stronger than before. I hope all these things for you. Because I know who you are. And because I know deep down inside you know who you are as well.

As we close the last chapter of 2023, I woke up thinking how I was feeling in the beginning of the year I was dealing with a lot. I feel like my whole world was collapsing right before my eyes I was very depressed. I was really in a dark place. Let’s just say life was lying for sure. And i knows lots of us felt this way this but guys we made at the end of the chapter. 

I have learned a lot about myself. I am committed to my personal growth. I am capable of rising above the challenge. When everybody else doubt me I’m always ready to prove somebody wrong. Tell me I can’t do it and I’m gonna show you I can. I am choosing my own health and happiness before anything. I am worthy of love, and everything else I desire. Thank you God for guiding me each and every day. I am grateful for everything that I have and the people in my life.
